'''亚铁氰化钾'''，俗称'''黄血盐'''，化学式为K<sub>4</sub>[Fe(CN)<sub>6</sub>]·3H<sub>2</sub>O，它是[[配位化合物|配位化合物]][Fe(CN)<sub>6</sub>]<sup>4−</sup>的钾盐。室温下为柠檬黄色[[单斜|单斜]]晶体。

==合成==
1752年，法国化学家[[皮埃尔·麦克尔|皮埃尔·约瑟夫·麦克尔]]首先报道了亚铁氰化钾的制备，他通过使[[普鲁士蓝|普鲁士蓝]]与[[氢氧化钾|氢氧化钾]]反应来实现。<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Macquer |title=Éxamen chymique de bleu de Prusse |journal=Histoire de l'Académie royale des sciences … , § Mémoires de l'Académie royale des Sciences |date=1752 |pages=60–77 |url=https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/item/88112#page/250/mode/1up |trans-title=Chemical examination of Prussian blue |language=fr |access-date=2022-01-29 |archive-date=2022-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220129082430/https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/item/88112#page/250/mode/1up |dead-url=no }} 
 From pp. 63-64:  ''"Après avoir essayé ainsi inutilement de décomposer le bleu de Prusse par les acides, … n'avoit plus qu'une couleur jaune un peu rousse."''  (After having tried so vainly to decompose Prussian blue by acids, I made recourse to alkalies.  I put a half ounce of this [Prussian] blue in a flask, and I poured on it ten ounces of a solution of nitre fixed by tartar [i.e., [[potassium_nitrate|potassium nitrate]] (''nitre'') which is mixed with crude [[potassium_bitartrate|cream of tartar]] and then ignited, producing potassium carbonate].  As soon as these two substances had been mixed together, I saw with astonishment that, without the aid of heat, the blue color had entirely disappeared; the powder [i.e., precipitate] at the bottom of the flask had only a rather gray color:  having put this vessel on a [[sand_bath|sand bath]] in order to heat the solution until it simmered, this gray color also disappeared entirely, and all that was contained in the flask, both the powder [i.e., precipitate] and the solution, had only a yellow color [that was] a little red.)</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Munroe |first1=Charles E. |last2=Chatard |first2=Thomas M. |title=Manufactures: Chemicals and Allied Products |journal=Twelfth Census of the United States: Bulletins |date=1902 |issue=210 |pages=1–306 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=8UIUAQAAMAAJ&pg=RA1-PA31 |access-date=2022-01-29 |archive-date=2022-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220129082430/https://books.google.com/books?id=8UIUAQAAMAAJ&pg=RA1-PA31 |dead-url=no }}; see p. 31.</ref>

===现代生产===
亚铁氰化钾在工业上由[[氰化氢|氰化氢]]、[[氯化亚铁|氯化亚铁]]和[[氢氧化钙|氢氧化钙]]生产，它们组合生成[[亚铁氰化钙|亚铁氰化钙]]Ca<sub>2</sub>[Fe(CN)<sub>6</sub>]·11H<sub>2</sub>O。然后用钾盐处理该溶液以沉淀混合的钾-钙盐CaK2[Fe(CN)6]，最后再用[[碳酸钾|碳酸钾]]处理得到钾盐。<ref name=Ullmann>{{ cite encyclopedia |author1=Gail, E. |author2=Gos, S. |author3=Kulzer, R. |author4=Lorösch, J. |author5=Rubo, A. |author6=Sauer, M. |author7=Kellens, R. |author8=Reddy, J. |author9=Steier, N. |author10=Hasenpusch, W. | title = Cyano Compounds, Inorganic | encyclopedia = Ullmann's Encyclopedia of Industrial Chemistry |date=October 2011 | publisher = Wiley-VCH | location = Weinheim | doi = 10.1002/14356007.a08_159.pub3 |isbn=978-3527306732 }}</ref>

===历史生产===
从历史上看，该化合物是由含有氮、铁和碳酸钾的有机化合物制成的。<ref name=Wagner>{{cite book|last=Von Wagner|first=Rudolf|title=Manual of chemical technology|year=1897|publisher=D. Appleton & Co.|location=New York|page=474 & 477|url=http://babel.hathitrust.org/cgi/pt?id=uc2.ark:/13960/t3tt4gz1p;view=1up;seq=502|access-date=2022-03-13|archive-date=2019-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190309132228/https://babel.hathitrust.org/cgi/pt?id=uc2.ark%3A%2F13960%2Ft3tt4gz1p%3Bview%3D1up%3Bseq%3D502|dead-url=no}}</ref>常见的[[氮|氮]]源和[[碳|碳]]源是[[焙烧|焙烧]]后的角、皮革废料、[[内脏|内脏]]或干血。它也可以从煤气厂的废氧化物（含有氰化氢）中获得。

==化学性质==
用[[硝酸|硝酸]]处理亚铁氰化钾可以得到H2[Fe(NO)(CN)5]。用[[碳酸钠|碳酸钠]]中和后，可以选择性地结晶出[[硝普钠|硝普钠]]的红色晶体。<ref>{{cite encyclopedia | author = Seel, F. | title = Sodium nitrosyl cyanoferrate | encyclopedia = Handbook of Preparative Inorganic Chemistry | edition = 2nd | editor = Brauer, G. | publisher = Academic Press | year = 1965 | location = New York | volume = 2 | page = 1768 | lccn = 63-14307 | url = https://www.scribd.com/doc/27443280/Handbook-of-Preparative-Inorganic-Chemistry-Vol-2-2d-Ed-George-Brauer | access-date = 2022-01-29 | archive-date = 2010-03-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100307011411/http://www.scribd.com/doc/27443280/Handbook-of-Preparative-Inorganic-Chemistry-Vol-2-2d-Ed-George-Brauer | dead-url = no }}</ref>

用[[氯气|氯气]]处理后，亚铁氰化钾可转化为[[铁氰化钾|铁氰化钾]]：
:2 K<sub>4</sub>[Fe(CN)<sub>6</sub>] + Cl<sub>2</sub> → 2 K<sub>3</sub>[Fe(CN)<sub>6</sub>] + 2 KCl
该反应可用于从溶液中去除亚铁氰化钾。{{citation needed|date=April 2012}}

亚铁氰化钾和铁盐反应生成[[普鲁士蓝|普鲁士蓝]]Fe{{su|p=3+|b=4}}[Fe{{su|p=2+}}CN){{su|b=6}}]{{su|b=3}}，这种物质是[[蓝图|蓝图]]颜色的来源。

==应用==
亚铁氰化钾在工业中有许多应用。它和[[亚铁氰化钠|其钠盐]]被广泛用作路盐和食盐的抗结剂。亚铁氰化钾和亚铁氰化钠也被用于锡的提纯和从钼矿石中分离铜。亚铁氰化钾可用于生产葡萄酒和柠檬酸。<ref name=Ullmann/>

截至2017年在[[欧盟|欧盟]]，亚铁氰酸盐(E 535–538)仅被授权在两个食品类别中作为盐替代品。[[肾|肾]]是亚铁氰酸盐毒性的器官。<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Peter Aggett, Fernando Aguilar, Riccardo Crebelli, Birgit Dusemund, Metka Filipič, Maria Jose Frutos, Pierre Galtier, David Gott, Ursula Gundert‐Remy, Gunter Georg Kuhnle, Claude Lambré, Jean‐Charles Leblanc, Inger Therese Lillegaard, Peter Moldeus, Alicja Mortensen, Agneta Oskarsson, Ivan Stankovic, Ine Waalkens‐Berendsen, Rudolf Antonius Woutersen, Matthew Wright and Maged Younes. |title=Re‐evaluation of sodium ferrocyanide (E 535), potassium ferrocyanide (E 536) and calcium ferrocyanide (E 538) as food additives |journal=EFSA Journal |date=2018 |volume=16 |issue=7 |page=5374 |doi=10.2903/j.efsa.2018.5374 |pmid=32626000 |pmc=7009536 |url=https://www.efsa.europa.eu/en/efsajournal/pub/5374 |doi-access=free |access-date=2022-01-29 |archive-date=2022-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220129110255/https://www.efsa.europa.eu/en/efsajournal/pub/5374 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

亚铁氰化钾可用于动物饲料。<ref>{{cite web |title=EuSalt Expert Meeting on E 535 and E 536 as Feed Additives |url=https://eusalt.com/events/eusalt-expert-meeting-e-535-and-e-536-feed-additives |publisher=EUSalt |access-date=2022-01-29 |archive-date=2019-05-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190512013808/https://eusalt.com/events/eusalt-expert-meeting-e-535-and-e-536-feed-additives |dead-url=no }}</ref>

在实验室中，亚铁氰化钾用于确定[[高锰酸钾|高锰酸钾]]的浓度，这种化合物通常用于[[氧化还原|氧化还原]][[滴定|滴定]]。
铁氰化钾与铁氰化钾和磷酸盐缓冲溶液混合使用，为[[β-半乳糖苷酶|β-半乳糖苷酶]]提供缓冲液，该酶用于裂解[[X-gal|X-gal]]，使与β-gal共轭的抗体（或其他分子）与目标结合的地方呈现出明亮的蓝色。
在与铁离子反应时，它会产生普鲁士蓝色。因此，它被用作实验室中铁的鉴定试剂。

亚铁氰化钾可用作植物的肥料。{{citation needed|date=April 2012}}

公元1900年前，在[[卡斯纳法|卡斯纳法]]发明之前，亚铁氰化钾是碱金属[[氰化物|氰化物]]的最重要来源。<ref name=Ullmann />在这个历史过程中，[[氰化钾|氰化钾]]是通过分解亚铁氰化钾产生的<ref name=Wagner />：

K<sub>4</sub>[Fe(CN)<sub>6</sub>] → 4 KCN + FeC<sub>2</sub> + N<sub>2</sub>

==结构==
与其他金属氰化物一样，亚铁氰化钾不管是水合物还是无水盐，都具有复杂的聚合结构。该聚合物由八面体 [Fe(CN)<sub>6</sub>]<sup>4−</sup>中心与CN[[配体|配体]]结合的K<sup>+</sup>离子交联。<ref>Willans, M.J.; Wasylishen, R.E.; McDonald, R. "Polymorphism of potassium ferrocyanide trihydrate as studied by solid-state multinuclear NMR spectroscopy and X-ray diffraction" Inorganic Chemistry 2009, volume 48, p4342-4353</ref>当固体溶解在水中时，K-CN键会断裂。{{citation needed|date=May 2020}}

===毒性===
亚铁氰化钾无毒，在体内不会分解为氰化物。对大鼠的毒性低，致死量 (LD<sub>50</sub>) 为6400mg/kg。<ref name=JTBaker>{{cite web | url = http://hazard.com/msds/mf/baker/baker/files/p5763.htm | title = POTASSIUM FERROCYANIDE MSDS Number: P5763 - Effective Date: 12/08/96 | publisher = J. T. Baker Inc. | access-date = 2012-04-08 | archive-date = 2015-11-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151121093949/http://hazard.com/msds/mf/baker/baker/files/p5763.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>

